text: Lindsay Lohan has checked into rehab in Newport Beach, Calif., and will remain there for the time being, pending an investigation of the facility she chose. This despite the fact that, at the 11th hour, Lohan bailed on rehab in a New York facility that was approved by prosecutors and a judge and flew to L.A.
title: Lindsay Lohan Checks Into Rehab in Newport Beach ; Investigation of Facility Pending.
